{"content": "I need to multiply 311 \u00d7 548 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 311\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 243 + 9 + 1 = 253\u2081\u2080\n- 548\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 405 + 36 + 8 = 449\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 253 \u00d7 449 = 113,597\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 113597 \u00f7 9 = 12621 r 8\n- 12621 \u00f7 9 = 1402 r 3\n- 1402 \u00f7 9 = 155 r 7\n- 155 \u00f7 9 = 17 r 2\n- 17 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 8\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **182738\u2089**\n\n182738", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}